" >Have a favorite breed of dog? Complete quests to unlock more dogs to walk! All dogs that are available to walk in Dog Walking Adventures are based on real life dogs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can see the descriptions and real life images of these dogs on the 'Dogs' page.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SOLVE PUZZLES & COMPLETE QUESTS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find and solve puzzles scattered throughout each map. Each map comes with a variety of puzzles to solve as well as quests to complete. </p>",
